{"type": "article", "id": 40541, "title": "你见过用纸做的“鸡尾酒”吗？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-05-07T22:31:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 34381, "name": "Studio Yumakano"}, {"id": 40179, "name": "Yelldesign"}, {"id": 40180, "name": "Papermeal"}, {"id": 40181, "name": "White Bear Studio"}, {"id": 40182, "name": "nHouse"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 79, "image": "img/article/article_show/2017050721420397jsa4P0wJD2KOSr.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p class=\"\">「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Cocktails by Yelldesign</h3><p>以定格动画见长的墨尔本动画工作室 <a href=\"http://www.yelldesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yelldesign</a> 在去年推出了一个名为 <a href=\"http://www.papermeal.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Papermeal</a> 的项目，用一系列栩栩如生的纸艺作品还原了<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/30252.html\">食物的制作过程</a>。最近，团队又以饮料为主题，对鸡尾酒的制作方式进行了一次类似的超现实演绎：比如，在制作 B-52 鸡尾酒时，整个过程就是在飞机上进行的，层次鲜明的三种酒分别来自娱乐系统的手柄、牙膏和眼罩，最后的点火则是由从天而降的氧气面罩完成的。整个 Cocktails 系列包含五部动画，由 9 位设计师耗时 3 个月完成。为了还原玻璃杯，他们使用了一系列半透明的纸张，以营造出磨砂感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507214135VmYM2ocQI53hPjgW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561628\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507214135BuiDwkads9EXlWy3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561628\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705072141357IiZ0OaCMvy6sQTH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561628\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507214135KleM5bT1gQxHnXZh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561628\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507214135AwuFrnHgSLKU9TWy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561628\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>NeoLucida XL by Pablo Gracia &amp; Golan Levin</h3><p>要想在没有工具帮助的情况下完成一张精确的素描并非易事，科学家 William Hyde Wollaston 为此在 19 世纪初发明了名为 camera lucida 的投影描绘仪，利用光学原理让画家可以透过镜子快速地将目标物体描绘出来。2013 年，来自芝加哥艺术学院的 Pablo Gracia 和 Golan Levin 教授就以它为原型设计了名为 NeoLucida 的复刻版。由于观测镜太小，很多集资者在收到后给出了希望增加视野范围的提议。在经历了两年的测试研发后，团队推出了这台名为 NeoLucida XL 的迭代款，除了加大了镜子之外，还新增了一片可以调节明暗度的小板子。仪器折叠后仅有 2.5 厘米的厚度，可以轻松地放进口袋里随身携带。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/pgarcia/neolucida-xl\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 60 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507214028vHsNfL1hpjXcPKDt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705072140283lLr6JYxKnzw45pB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.730882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507214029hHUB8Cm3gKs5wTax.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.813235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507214028AmVOpfX5T1Gz2a4P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507214028zhMl6QZ0BHwO3dGc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>EcoQube Frame by Aqua Design Innovations</h3><p>想在家里种点小型蔬菜或是香料却苦于没有足够的空间？最近，一支致力于建设水生生态系统的设计团队 Aqua Design Innovations 研发了名为 EcoQube Frame 的垂直水栽种植板，在提升空间利用率的同时将原本复杂的种植简化为浇水和播种两个步骤，让忙碌的上班族不用经常操心植物的情况。根据团队介绍，播种后只要十天时间就能收获蔬菜。除了桌面之外，种植板也支持上墙放置。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/kevinzl/ecoqube-frame-best-vertical-garden\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 49 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507214010XocO7SH84yqa0vCZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.549412\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507214010bXcdLWrSxEPBNgly.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.478824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507214010STfgH3wbq5Akp0O1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.588235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507214010Wx8FVKUglvdY17mf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.524706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>On Bicycle Stand by Studio Yumakano</h3><p>针对自行车随意摆放的这一城市顽疾，日本设计工作室 <a href=\"http://yumakano.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studio Yumakano</a> 推出了一套以自行车为原型设计的停车支架。由金属片构成的这三款迷你自行车重 1.5 千克，可以根据需要放置在户外，既是停车位又起到了标识的作用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507213947T5LN34wPeYsGJZMi.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507213947KzpPUMmNX1JeC3u6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507213947X0AhbD38rHGuvB1f.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705072139488a6hnCXyMj2ZE5AP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Hair Dryer by WV design</h3><p>因为厌倦了吹风机那总是缠绕在一起的电线，韩国设计团队 WV design 决定对传统的吹风机结构进行拆分，打造了一个集不同几何形功能组件的概念产品。使用时，只要轻按底座上的按钮就可以在解锁手柄的同时展开隐藏在内部的电线。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507213910l0YyRf7OVurbpJaD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.177262\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507213910FeW6Rr57aTUI0oOz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.781174\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705072139107HxX6BdEMZhoa5yz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.735941\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507213911SsabrNUVt52vjgBO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.991443\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507213911E8sdLhpImKYCTxev.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>nHouse by White Bear Studio</h3><p>nHouse 是一个英国的模块化房屋公司，它的主要业务是在建造出两层楼高的三居室房屋后再将其运输到客户指定的位置。为了强调公司对房屋细节的一丝不苟和简约的设计风格，操刀品牌设计的 <a href=\"http://whitebearstudio.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">White Bear Studio </a>为它设计了一个像是房屋轮廓的 logo，同时又能代表品牌名中的 n。在相关的宣传资料上，logo 本身则被细分成了 4 种形状的镂空，激发客户的好奇心。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507213850vVGns0YuHPjc3RMq.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605333\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507213851BHOipeI2AYK4ChU9.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507213850FV2xLdIDYOv54H8t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507213851YVL3oe5217anmI4P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170507213850RzA5EZ8lJWI0PKce.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>"}